1
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,720
Let's go eat.

2
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,230
Sorry, I gotta go.

3
00:00:55,950 --> 00:00:58,340
Oh, okay. Never mind.

4
00:00:59,180 --> 00:00:59,750
What?

5
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:03,400
I wanted to try that new ramen shop.

6
00:01:05,170 --> 00:01:06,280
Oh, it wasn't so good.

7
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:11,430
I'll go home, then.

8
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,350
Seeing your big bro?

9
00:01:13,350 --> 00:01:14,100
Yup.

10
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,540
Gotta borrow money.

11
00:01:19,190 --> 00:01:22,390
So it's the end of the month already.

12
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:05,660
I felt as if summer would last forever.

13
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:12,560
The next season seemed like it'd never come even after September.

14
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:20,600
And your bird can sing

15
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,910
- I'm off. - See ya.

16
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,370
Drinks later?

17
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,060
I have other plans.

18
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,500
Next time, then.

19
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:54,450
Thanks for filling in.

20
00:02:54,830 --> 00:02:56,290
Oh, no problem at all.

21
00:02:57,330 --> 00:02:59,830
But it's about time he got fired.

22
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:02,750
He's irresponsible not showing up.

23
00:03:03,540 --> 00:03:04,760
You may be right.

24
00:03:07,210 --> 00:03:09,050
I saw your watch in a magazine.

25
00:03:09,050 --> 00:03:10,150
It's cool.

26
00:03:10,770 --> 00:03:11,620
See ya.

27
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:14,540
Mizuki, drinks tonight?

28
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:16,990
Sorry I have a date.

29
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:19,260
- Next time, then. - Sorry.

30
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:20,260
See you, Boss.

31
00:03:21,050 --> 00:03:22,220
Thanks, guys.

32
00:03:57,180 --> 00:03:57,850
Hey.

33
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:02,950
Good evening.

34
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,000
What are you doing?

35
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,560
Huh?

36
00:04:10,180 --> 00:04:11,420
Why'd you skip work?

37
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,430
Well...

38
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,210
Early shift tomorrow?

39
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:21,250
Yes.

40
00:04:23,030 --> 00:04:23,950
You better come.

41
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:28,510
Good night.

42
00:05:01,730 --> 00:05:11,080
One, two, three, four, five...

43
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:18,080
11, 12, 13, 14, 15...

44
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:21,570
I'd never waited for a girl who I didn't know well.

45
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:23,390
21, 22,

46
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:25,580
I could've gotten the wrong idea,

47
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:29,570
so I decided to leave on the count of 120.

48
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:31,380
29, 30

49
00:05:31,380 --> 00:05:33,450
I just had to take a chance.

50
00:05:33,450 --> 00:05:40,860
33, 34, 3, 36, 37, 38, 39, 40,

51
00:05:41,410 --> 00:05:50,750
41, 42, 43, 44, 45, 46, 47, 48, 49,

52
00:05:54,680 --> 00:06:01,840
113, 114, 115, 116, 117...

53
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:04,040
It worked.

54
00:06:04,890 --> 00:06:06,140
You read my mind.

55
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,870
What were you doing?

56
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:17,400
I just got out of the movie theater.

57
00:06:18,810 --> 00:06:19,890
Take me next time.

58
00:06:20,370 --> 00:06:21,460
Sure.

59
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,510
Where's the boss?

60
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:33,320
Don't worry about him.

61
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:34,800
It doesn't matter.

62
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,100
Got a light?

63
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,300
You smoke, right?

64
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,170
Here.

65
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,650
Why don't we go for a drink?

66
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:57,230
Where's your spot?

67
00:06:58,350 --> 00:07:01,030
Well, do you know Suginoko?

68
00:07:01,910 --> 00:07:02,990
Kind of.

69
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:05,930
I gotta go home first, so meet me there.

70
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:07,170
- What time? - Let's see.

71
00:07:07,170 --> 00:07:13,530
Maybe around 10. I'll text you.

72
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:16,670
- You have my number? - No.

73
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:22,510
Give it.

74
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,590
- What? - Nothing.

75
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:42,150
Here.

76
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:44,640
I'll text you.

77
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:46,480
- Promise? - Yup.

78
00:07:58,530 --> 00:08:00,200
I'm home.

79
00:08:40,070 --> 00:08:41,200
You got some?

80
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,740
- Money? - Yeah.

81
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:46,610
Don't you get that thing?

82
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:51,630
- What? - The thing! You know.

83
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:53,330
- Unemployment benefits? - That's it.

84
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:55,810
It got cut off.

85
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:59,780
Oh, that's terrible.

86
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:04,150
I wanted to borrow a little.

87
00:09:04,490 --> 00:09:06,630
Ask your other son for money.

88
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,400
Anyway.

89
00:09:14,650 --> 00:09:16,700
When I go senile,

90
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:21,250
I don't want you to get me treatment.

91
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:24,740
Want me to kill you?

92
00:09:24,990 --> 00:09:27,010
Right. Kill me.

93
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,480
Gotcha.

94
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:30,830
Wow. Just like that, huh?

95
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,880
I don't think you can, though.

96
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:38,480
What do you mean?

97
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:50,960
Stop shaking your leg.

98
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:53,760
Stop nagging me.

99
00:09:55,490 --> 00:09:56,460
What?

100
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,770
You drink too much.

101
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,960
You might really become senile.

102
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:11,360
Don't worry about me.

103
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,340
You're so sweet, Shizuo.

104
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,700
I love you.

105
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:49,150
Morning.

106
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,490
Oh, well.

107
00:11:42,310 --> 00:11:43,550
I lied earlier.

108
00:11:45,860 --> 00:11:47,290
I didn't see my brother,

109
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,010
I ran into my mom at a pub.

110
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:53,940
Oh. But wasn't she in the hospital?

111
00:11:54,530 --> 00:11:56,760
She's out and staying at my brothers.

112
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,780
That's good.

113
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:01,790
I'm not sure..

114
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:03,940
It's not easy.

115
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,280
Give me that.

116
00:12:43,830 --> 00:12:44,130
What?

117
00:12:44,130 --> 00:12:45,340
Come closer.

118
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:46,420
Come here.

119
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:47,750
Stand there.

120
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:50,560
What are you doing?

121
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,300
Smell them.

122
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:55,400
They're real.

123
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,850
They do smell nice.

124
00:12:58,580 --> 00:12:59,830
These don't.

125
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:02,690
What are they doing here?

126
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:11,490
You wanna carry that?

127
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:12,510
Let me help.

128
00:13:12,510 --> 00:13:14,540
You dropped a leaf.

129
00:13:14,540 --> 00:13:15,720
Hold on, wait.

130
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,590
You're gonna fall over.

131
00:13:17,950 --> 00:13:21,040
Just lift this up straight...

132
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:22,570
See? I got this.

133
00:13:28,730 --> 00:13:30,710
Hey, that's scary!

134
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:33,540
Looks like it's walking, huh?

135
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,230
It's getting heavy.

136
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:39,160
Good.

137
00:13:48,620 --> 00:13:52,440
Here's your change and receipt.

138
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,100
Thank you.

139
00:13:59,450 --> 00:14:00,630
Next, please.

140
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:09,950
Hey.

141
00:14:13,310 --> 00:14:14,680
You smell like booze.

142
00:14:18,390 --> 00:14:22,780
Is this the hipster style that's in fashion now?

143
00:14:22,780 --> 00:14:23,760
No, not really.

144
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:27,330
At least get a pair of leather shoes.

145
00:14:38,260 --> 00:14:38,920
Hey.

146
00:14:40,190 --> 00:14:41,640
Don't you have something to say?

147
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:42,670
What?

148
00:14:43,780 --> 00:14:46,270
Your ditching causes others trouble.

149
00:14:48,180 --> 00:14:51,650
I didn't feel well, so I was sleeping all day.

150
00:14:55,130 --> 00:14:56,930
You're such a liar.

151
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:22,030
Thanks for the lighter.

152
00:16:25,230 --> 00:16:25,860
Oh, keep it.

153
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:32,250
Did you go to the pub yesterday?

154
00:16:34,920 --> 00:16:37,190
Yeah, of course.

155
00:16:38,730 --> 00:16:40,030
Did you talk to Motoko?

156
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,500
It's a good pub.

157
00:16:47,850 --> 00:16:49,730
I like her, the owner.

158
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:55,430
We were talking trash about you.

159
00:16:57,230 --> 00:16:58,700
What's wrong with me?

160
00:17:04,150 --> 00:17:05,590
You broke your promise.

161
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:10,010
I fell asleep.

162
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:14,010
And?

163
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:18,950
I got up and drank till dawn.

164
00:17:23,390 --> 00:17:24,180
Are you upset?

165
00:17:25,410 --> 00:17:25,940
No.

166
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:28,610
Just surprised.

167
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:30,720
Sorry.

168
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:37,950
You really are insincere.

169
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,110
Insincere?

170
00:17:41,470 --> 00:17:42,690
Insincere huh...

171
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,490
Did you drink alone?

172
00:17:47,490 --> 00:17:49,960
No, with someone I live with.

173
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,140
So you got a girlfriend?

174
00:17:53,140 --> 00:17:54,060
Guy friend.

175
00:17:56,430 --> 00:17:58,310
It's cheaper to split the rent.

176
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:02,530
What's your life like?

177
00:18:03,340 --> 00:18:04,360
You know.

178
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:07,180
I'm just a part-timer at a bookstore.

179
00:18:10,510 --> 00:18:11,100
Hey.

180
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:13,880
On your face.

181
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:17,040
Gross.

182
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:20,070
Here, use this.

183
00:18:24,430 --> 00:18:25,210
Thank you.

184
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:35,740
Do you want this?

185
00:18:36,370 --> 00:18:37,140
Can I?

186
00:18:38,130 --> 00:18:39,080
Thanks.

187
00:18:43,470 --> 00:18:44,290
Okay, thank you.

188
00:18:44,970 --> 00:18:46,190
I can't keep this.

189
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:47,510
It's okay.

190
00:18:48,410 --> 00:18:49,210
You don't need it?

191
00:18:49,210 --> 00:18:49,890
No.

192
00:18:49,890 --> 00:18:50,500
Really?

193
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:52,730
I'll keep it then.

194
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,690
Thanks for this.

195
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,120
It's good.

196
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:23,990
"Thanks for the sandwich"

197
00:19:34,410 --> 00:19:35,380
Welcome.

198
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:25,480
Over there.

199
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:54,630
I don't want any drama.

200
00:21:03,390 --> 00:21:04,280
Don't worry.

201
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,650
No drama.

202
00:21:13,420 --> 00:21:15,270
Just a second, it's hot.

203
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:23,080
It's cramped here.

204
00:21:23,710 --> 00:21:24,470
Floor?

205
00:21:25,090 --> 00:21:25,690
It's okay.

206
00:21:25,690 --> 00:21:26,580
You sure?

207
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:43,100
Oh wait, there's a bug.

208
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:44,400
Don't move.

209
00:21:52,820 --> 00:21:53,810
You're not gonna kill it?

210
00:21:54,810 --> 00:21:56,760
My friend hates it when I do.

211
00:21:57,970 --> 00:21:58,900
Keep it open.

212
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,480
- Oh, hey. - Huh?

213
00:22:12,290 --> 00:22:13,290
You got a rubber?

214
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:24,980
What are you doing?

215
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:26,500
Get down first.

216
00:22:27,730 --> 00:22:29,170
It hurts.

217
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:33,790
Here.

218
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:34,620
Thanks.

219
00:22:38,190 --> 00:22:39,150
Hurry.

220
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:19,820
What?

221
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,220
Got it.

222
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:42,000
Was that your friend just now?

223
00:23:43,050 --> 00:23:44,150
Yeah, probably.

224
00:23:45,320 --> 00:23:46,280
You heard?

225
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,010
Yeah. I feel bad.

226
00:23:49,450 --> 00:23:50,240
He's fine.

227
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:52,840
I hope so.

228
00:24:27,110 --> 00:24:28,200
Oh hey, you're back.

229
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:31,210
He's the one I told you about.

230
00:24:33,150 --> 00:24:34,120
I'm Shizuo.

231
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,120
I'm Sachiko. Nice to meet you.

232
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,460
Nice to meet you.

233
00:24:52,390 --> 00:24:53,400
Want a tomato?

234
00:24:54,150 --> 00:24:56,200
No, I'm fine. I'll just have a drink.

235
00:25:03,370 --> 00:25:05,100
It's quiet next door.

236
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:07,680
Yeah, haven't heard any noise today.

237
00:25:08,540 --> 00:25:09,400
That's good.

238
00:25:10,430 --> 00:25:11,500
What's that about?

239
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:14,300
It's not that interesting.

240
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:18,000
- Oh, shall we? - Oh, yeah.

241
00:25:19,900 --> 00:25:21,600
Cheers.

242
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,400
How did you guys meet?

243
00:25:33,930 --> 00:25:35,120
We work at the same bookstore.

244
00:25:44,840 --> 00:25:45,780
And you guys?

245
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:49,130
We worked in the same factory.

246
00:25:50,210 --> 00:25:51,050
Oh, what kind?

247
00:25:51,380 --> 00:25:52,120
Ice cream.

248
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:54,400
Sounds like fun.

249
00:25:55,220 --> 00:25:56,100
It was pretty rough.

250
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:59,900
We were working in a giant freezer,

251
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:04,540
so we had to be dressed like Eskimos.

252
00:26:13,990 --> 00:26:15,580
Good evening.

253
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:16,880
- I'll take that. - Thank you.

254
00:27:33,900 --> 00:27:36,600
Oh, we're out of soda.

255
00:27:36,600 --> 00:27:37,700
Okay.

256
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,540
- How much? - It's already 1,500 yen.

257
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:47,750
Now it's 2,000 yen,

258
00:27:47,750 --> 00:27:48,820
Damn it.

259
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,800
I put toilet paper in.

260
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:57,400
It's for our place.

261
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,390
I don't have enough.

262
00:28:00,390 --> 00:28:01,400
What?

263
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:02,090
Just kidding.

264
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:08,300
She'll regret offering to pay.

265
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:13,090
The total is 3,219 yen.

266
00:28:13,090 --> 00:28:14,150
We bought a lot.

267
00:28:14,770 --> 00:28:16,480
I only have a big bill.

268
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:17,880
Thank you.

269
00:28:59,950 --> 00:29:01,810
Oh, you're getting there.

270
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:06,280
Watch out for your tongue.

271
00:29:09,540 --> 00:29:10,700
Mouth harps?

272
00:29:17,690 --> 00:29:18,320
Look.

273
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:32,510
Did you really need to stop him for that?

274
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:37,400
Does that really count?

275
00:29:38,390 --> 00:29:40,890
She does it better than I do.

276
00:29:40,890 --> 00:29:42,480
I'm not so sure about that.

277
00:29:43,190 --> 00:29:44,150
- Here. - Thanks.

278
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:45,840
Have some ice.

279
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:49,920
It's cold.

280
00:29:50,610 --> 00:29:51,700
Doesn't it feel nice?

281
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,480
Let me try.

282
00:30:00,450 --> 00:30:01,600
Can you do it?

283
00:30:02,140 --> 00:30:03,200
I can do it.

284
00:30:08,190 --> 00:30:09,010
Not.

285
00:30:09,010 --> 00:30:10,300
Give me a second.

286
00:30:11,020 --> 00:30:11,980
You suck.

287
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:24,710
Are the trains still running?

288
00:30:27,610 --> 00:30:28,180
Yeah.

289
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,600
It's okay, I'll clean up later.

290
00:30:47,260 --> 00:30:48,460
Stay over tonight.

291
00:30:52,130 --> 00:30:53,490
I'm going home.

292
00:31:02,390 --> 00:31:03,810
Leaving already?

293
00:31:04,970 --> 00:31:05,810
Yeah, I'm leaving.

294
00:31:06,810 --> 00:31:07,970
Hey, Sachiko.

295
00:31:10,020 --> 00:31:10,750
What?

