Sometimes I don't know what he's thinking.

589
01:06:55,580 --> 01:06:56,710
That's probably because

590
01:06:58,160 --> 01:07:00,020
he's really not thinking anything.

591
01:07:09,000 --> 01:07:10,140
Is everything okay?

592
01:07:15,330 --> 01:07:16,640
Things led to things.

593
01:07:18,790 --> 01:07:20,520
How can I explain this?

594
01:07:26,590 --> 01:07:27,190
Just a bunch of stuff

595
01:07:28,480 --> 01:07:29,690
I can't figure out.

596
01:07:31,760 --> 01:07:32,490
Look.

597
01:07:32,930 --> 01:07:35,540
I burned a hole with a cigarette by accident.

598
01:07:36,820 --> 01:07:37,840
Nice shirt.

599
01:07:38,540 --> 01:07:39,250
Really?

600
01:07:39,250 --> 01:07:40,090
I like it a lot.

601
01:07:40,860 --> 01:07:41,610
Thank you.

602
01:07:50,000 --> 01:07:52,840
It was all my fault. I apologize.

603
01:07:54,980 --> 01:07:55,880
What are you talking about?

604
01:07:57,110 --> 01:08:00,880
I told him about the th... th... thief.

605
01:08:02,540 --> 01:08:04,000
That you let him run away.

606
01:08:07,140 --> 01:08:09,240
I know you just got chewed out.

607
01:08:11,570 --> 01:08:13,400
I want us to be cool.

608
01:08:18,410 --> 01:08:19,380
Let's make peace.

609
01:08:21,180 --> 01:08:22,280
I don't care.

610
01:08:29,920 --> 01:08:31,670
Okay. We're good, then.

611
01:08:45,760 --> 01:08:48,230
We gotta fill in Sachiko's spot.

612
01:08:55,680 --> 01:08:59,770
I saw Sachiko and the boss together last night.

613
01:09:00,350 --> 01:09:02,280
They must be dating.

614
01:09:02,700 --> 01:09:04,810
Those scums are having fun

615
01:09:05,180 --> 01:09:07,580
while we're working hard.

616
01:09:07,580 --> 01:09:08,050
What?

617
01:09:08,940 --> 01:09:09,730
I said,

618
01:09:10,050 --> 01:09:12,300
we're the only ones working hard.

619
01:09:12,300 --> 01:09:14,390
People like them are scum.

620
01:09:18,140 --> 01:09:19,710
Am I right?

621
01:09:28,740 --> 01:09:31,480
Don't tell me you liked Sachiko, too?

622
01:09:38,350 --> 01:09:40,000
You just don't get it.

623
01:09:50,320 --> 01:09:51,060
It hurts.

624
01:09:52,830 --> 01:09:55,920
I'm sorry. Sorry.

625
01:10:10,740 --> 01:10:12,460
Your mom is calling.

626
01:10:12,460 --> 01:10:12,990
Oh.

627
01:10:20,320 --> 01:10:22,240
Why don't you ever pick up?

628
01:10:37,770 --> 01:10:38,600
Hey, Sachiko.

629
01:10:40,650 --> 01:10:42,270
Am I getting in between you two?

630
01:10:44,300 --> 01:10:46,230
Stop talking nonsense.

631
01:10:49,350 --> 01:10:58,410
I listen to my favorite song Alone, just like I used to

632
01:11:00,540 --> 01:11:12,680
Olivia has always given my lonely heart Comfort and consolation

633
01:11:14,830 --> 01:11:24,050
With a cup of jasmine tea I think I can sleep well tonight.

634
01:11:25,990 --> 01:11:38,850
All I want is to end the night The way I want it to

635
01:11:39,370 --> 01:11:50,160
I'd never expected a day like this Would ever come when we first met.

636
01:11:52,190 --> 01:11:54,830
Making good things better

637
01:11:54,830 --> 01:12:04,150
No, those days are gone Time has passed, we have changed.

638
01:12:04,150 --> 01:12:18,350
The love we had wore us down Because you only loved my illusion

639
01:12:27,910 --> 01:12:29,030
We're back.

640
01:12:33,270 --> 01:12:34,920
So stuffy.

641
01:12:48,340 --> 01:12:49,700
Be quiet.

642
01:12:52,780 --> 01:12:54,220
When did you get back?

643
01:12:55,510 --> 01:12:56,680
I don't remember.

644
01:12:57,480 --> 01:12:58,400
What time was it?

645
01:13:02,490 --> 01:13:03,690
Did we wake you up?

646
01:13:04,360 --> 01:13:04,900
No.

647
01:13:07,710 --> 01:13:09,250
Shizuo was pretty loud.

648
01:13:11,350 --> 01:13:12,390
I was dead asleep.

649
01:13:15,520 --> 01:13:16,460
That's good.

650
01:13:18,830 --> 01:13:20,320
You should've come.

651
01:13:23,800 --> 01:13:26,320
I just can't get into karaoke.

652
01:13:43,890 --> 01:13:45,330
You just lied.

653
01:13:46,230 --> 01:13:46,830
What?

654
01:13:48,180 --> 01:13:51,130
When we came back last night,

655
01:13:51,130 --> 01:13:52,250
were you actually awake?

656
01:13:55,670 --> 01:13:57,220
As if I was jealous?

657
01:13:57,960 --> 01:13:58,510
What?

658
01:13:59,180 --> 01:14:00,180
You got it. I was.

659
01:14:01,080 --> 01:14:02,600
Stop it.

660
01:14:03,240 --> 01:14:04,740
You're the one who asked.

661
01:14:06,330 --> 01:14:06,940
Excuse me.

662
01:14:17,440 --> 01:14:18,580
I'm going to work.

663
01:14:20,100 --> 01:14:20,640
Hey.

664
01:14:22,520 --> 01:14:24,540
Did the boss say anything about me?

665
01:14:25,830 --> 01:14:26,330
Yeah.

666
01:14:28,070 --> 01:14:28,770
What?

667
01:14:32,590 --> 01:14:34,800
He told me to take care of you.

668
01:14:36,310 --> 01:14:37,430
What did you say?

669
01:14:39,400 --> 01:14:40,440
Oh, nothing.

670
01:14:44,830 --> 01:14:46,260
Why is that?

671
01:14:49,870 --> 01:14:50,610
What?

672
01:14:52,030 --> 01:14:53,310
What's that look for?

673
01:15:00,620 --> 01:15:01,670
Then I'm going out.

674
01:15:02,420 --> 01:15:03,440
Have fun camping.

675
01:15:19,020 --> 01:15:19,820
He left already?

676
01:15:20,420 --> 01:15:20,940
Yeah.

677
01:15:21,480 --> 01:15:22,330
Okay.

678
01:15:23,280 --> 01:15:24,550
Did he take his umbrella?

679
01:15:26,040 --> 01:15:26,620
No.

680
01:15:27,840 --> 01:15:29,410
I don't think it'll rain today.

681
01:15:29,410 --> 01:15:30,990
The weather's unpredictable around this time.

682
01:15:31,630 --> 01:15:32,670
True.

683
01:15:42,610 --> 01:15:43,640
Want some coffee?

684
01:15:44,790 --> 01:15:46,120
Yeah, I'll have some.

685
01:16:29,160 --> 01:16:29,610
Hey.

686
01:16:36,140 --> 01:16:37,140
Not budging.

687
01:16:55,450 --> 01:16:56,480
Let me do it.

688
01:16:58,720 --> 01:17:02,260
You tie this one like this...

689
01:17:05,040 --> 01:17:06,100
Done.

690
01:17:11,720 --> 01:17:14,480
I'm Hasegawa. Nice to meet you.

691
01:17:14,480 --> 01:17:15,540
Likewise

692
01:17:15,540 --> 01:17:17,430
I forgot to wear pants.

693
01:17:17,840 --> 01:17:18,950
Oh, it's fine.

694
01:17:22,460 --> 01:17:23,030
Come with me.

695
01:17:26,910 --> 01:17:27,590
This way.

696
01:17:37,830 --> 01:17:41,230
I couldn't reach Moriguchi all day.

697
01:17:41,230 --> 01:17:42,470
Maybe he quit.

698
01:17:43,160 --> 01:17:44,480
I don't think so.

699
01:17:45,610 --> 01:17:48,170
It's unlikely for someone his age.

700
01:17:48,490 --> 01:17:50,090
I couldn't care less.

701
01:17:55,430 --> 01:17:58,270
You didn't do anything to him, did you?

702
01:17:59,110 --> 01:17:59,940
No way.

703
01:18:05,780 --> 01:18:07,130
Remember to lock the door.

704
01:18:07,130 --> 01:18:08,610
Okay. See you.

705
01:18:12,220 --> 01:18:13,650
I'm home.

706
01:19:22,050 --> 01:19:24,220
"Sorry, we're closed today. Suginoko"

707
01:20:03,240 --> 01:20:04,040
Sit down!

708
01:20:04,620 --> 01:20:05,640
Sit down!

709
01:20:08,040 --> 01:20:09,890
What?

710
01:20:09,890 --> 01:20:12,500
What do you want?

711
01:20:13,020 --> 01:20:13,700
I hate you!

712
01:20:18,400 --> 01:20:18,970
Ow!

713
01:20:23,030 --> 01:20:23,470
It hurts.

714
01:20:26,430 --> 01:20:27,420
Ow.

715
01:20:40,810 --> 01:20:41,290
No way.

716
01:20:43,290 --> 01:20:45,620
Wake up.

717
01:20:52,000 --> 01:20:52,890
Ouch.

718
01:21:01,460 --> 01:21:02,560
What's the hell?

719
01:21:02,900 --> 01:21:03,710
Ouch.

720
01:21:09,060 --> 01:21:09,970
It hurts.

721
01:21:17,240 --> 01:21:18,100
What the hell was that?

722
01:21:45,620 --> 01:21:46,470
It's cold.

723
01:21:47,650 --> 01:21:48,780
Damn it.

724
01:22:19,680 --> 01:22:20,900
Shizuo?

725
01:22:28,170 --> 01:22:29,990
Are you Shizuo's mother?

726
01:22:31,840 --> 01:22:32,480
Yes.

727
01:22:34,240 --> 01:22:35,210
Is there a problem?

728
01:22:37,870 --> 01:22:41,420
He never picks up his phone

729
01:22:42,540 --> 01:22:44,190
and doesn't return my texts.

730
01:22:44,670 --> 01:22:46,200
I'll let him call when he's back.

731
01:22:47,060 --> 01:22:48,380
He's been away?

732
01:22:48,380 --> 01:22:49,580
He went camping.

733
01:22:53,140 --> 01:22:57,530
Without working. What in the world is he doing?

734
01:23:02,430 --> 01:23:03,700
Those cuts...

735
01:23:04,560 --> 01:23:05,680
Did my son do that?

736
01:23:05,680 --> 01:23:06,640
Oh, no.

737
01:23:08,250 --> 01:23:09,740
Did you clean them?

738
01:23:10,530 --> 01:23:12,560
- Let me help. - No, I'm fine.

739
01:23:12,560 --> 01:23:13,630
It'll heal soon.

740
01:23:14,820 --> 01:23:15,550
You're right.

741
01:23:15,550 --> 01:23:16,280
Ok.

742
01:23:18,400 --> 01:23:19,000
Bye.

743
01:23:22,130 --> 01:23:26,170
Can you not tell Shizuo

744
01:23:26,740 --> 01:23:29,300
that I came here?

745
01:23:29,300 --> 01:23:30,240
Of course.

746
01:23:32,240 --> 01:23:32,810
Bye.

747
01:23:35,420 --> 01:23:36,760
Wait a second!

748
01:23:55,900 --> 01:23:57,800
Please accept this.

749
01:24:10,520 --> 01:24:11,590
You're a good kid.

750
01:24:13,880 --> 01:24:16,310
Don't worry about him too much.

751
01:24:17,450 --> 01:24:19,500
He knows what he's doing.

752
01:24:21,150 --> 01:24:23,710
You think so?

753
01:24:28,770 --> 01:24:29,400
Goodbye.

754
01:25:00,890 --> 01:25:01,750
You have work hard.

755
01:25:03,770 --> 01:25:05,110
We're leaving.

756
01:25:05,260 --> 01:25:06,390
See you.

757
01:25:06,390 --> 01:25:08,440
Would you like to have a drink with us?

758
01:25:11,660 --> 01:25:12,780
I'll come if I can.

759
01:25:12,780 --> 01:25:14,880
See you later.

760
01:25:16,880 --> 01:25:19,110
See you.

761
01:25:22,580 --> 01:25:23,580
Oh really?

762
01:25:35,980 --> 01:25:36,670
Okay.

763
01:25:49,290 --> 01:25:51,440
No, I won't.

764
01:25:54,790 --> 01:25:55,840
I'm home.

765
01:25:56,390 --> 01:25:57,100
Welcome home.

766
01:25:58,580 --> 01:25:59,420
Welcome home.

767
01:26:00,640 --> 01:26:01,740
How was camping?

768
01:26:03,800 --> 01:26:04,700
Exhausting.

769
01:26:07,570 --> 01:26:08,730
Was Shizuo there?

770
01:26:09,010 --> 01:26:10,190
Yeah, on the phone.

771
01:26:11,690 --> 01:26:12,970
Looks like his brother is calling.

772
01:26:12,970 --> 01:26:14,020
Really?

773
01:26:24,840 --> 01:26:26,040
What was it about?

774
01:26:26,510 --> 01:26:28,060
My mom collapsed.

775
01:26:32,290 --> 01:26:33,160
Really?

776
01:26:33,160 --> 01:26:35,360
Yeah. She had a seizure.

777
01:26:43,620 --> 01:26:44,620
Is she okay?

778
01:26:44,950 --> 01:26:46,250
I don't know.

779
01:26:46,830 --> 01:26:48,450
But she won't die.

780
01:26:52,150 --> 01:26:53,000
You're lying.

781
01:26:54,050 --> 01:26:55,610
Why would I lie?

782
01:26:55,610 --> 01:27:00,250
Because I saw her. Two days ago.

783
01:27:00,910 --> 01:27:01,720
My mother?

784
01:27:01,720 --> 01:27:03,930
She came to see you.

785
01:27:06,740 --> 01:27:08,340
Was she fine then?

786
01:27:10,510 --> 01:27:13,120
Well, she didn't look sick.

787
01:27:14,810 --> 01:27:18,200
But she was real worried about you, Shizuo.

788
01:27:23,620 --> 01:27:24,390
You going there?

789
01:27:24,980 --> 01:27:26,430
There are no trains now.

790
01:27:26,430 --> 01:27:27,750
I'll see her tomorrow morning.

791
01:27:36,740 --> 01:27:37,500
Good idea.

792
01:27:50,520 --> 01:27:52,810
It'd be best for her to die instantly.

793
01:27:52,810 --> 01:27:53,440
What?

794
01:27:55,220 --> 01:27:56,730
It's too much hassle.

795
01:27:59,000 --> 01:28:00,320
I guess karma got me.

796
01:28:02,060 --> 01:28:03,350
What karma?

797
01:28:03,770 --> 01:28:08,000
For hanging out and drinking every day like this.

798
01:28:11,060 --> 01:28:12,830
Don't think about it.

799
01:28:16,850 --> 01:28:19,040
What's wrong with hanging out?

800
01:28:19,810 --> 01:28:21,610
Don't be so childish.

801
01:28:23,010 --> 01:28:24,080
Am I wrong?

802
01:28:26,100 --> 01:28:27,660
You just don't get it.

803
01:28:28,250 --> 01:28:29,490
Sachiko's next.

804
01:28:41,150 --> 01:28:42,070
Wanna leave?

805
01:28:42,580 --> 01:28:43,980
Who wanted to drink?

806
01:28:43,980 --> 01:28:44,860
You did.

807
01:28:44,860 --> 01:28:45,830
No, you.

808
01:28:49,120 --> 01:28:50,070
Go ahead, Sachiko.

809
01:28:53,110 --> 01:28:54,090
Let's go home.

810
01:28:57,080 --> 01:28:58,320
Let's get some rest

811
01:28:59,050 --> 01:29:01,540
and go see his mom together.

812
01:29:01,540 --> 01:29:02,390
You're coming?

813
01:29:02,810 --> 01:29:03,720
I can't?

814
01:29:03,720 --> 01:29:04,720
I don't mind.

815
01:29:06,790 --> 01:29:09,550
But she probably won't be able to recognize anybody.

816
01:29:11,730 --> 01:29:13,140
I'll just go alone.

817
01:29:16,660 --> 01:29:20,430
When you come back, let's all drink together again.

818
01:29:23,000 --> 01:29:24,110
Get some sleep.

819
01:29:25,440 --> 01:29:27,230
Can't we drink now?

820
01:29:27,230 --> 01:29:29,600
You just said it's not a problem.

821
01:29:44,210 --> 01:29:45,410
That was close.

822
01:29:45,410 --> 01:29:48,240
It almost hit the center.

823
01:29:48,610 --> 01:29:50,830
I almost got the center.

824
01:29:50,830 --> 01:29:52,160
One eye closed works really well.

825
01:29:59,780 --> 01:30:00,930
I'll just keep going.

826
01:30:04,560 --> 01:30:06,640
You crack me up.

827
01:30:07,480 --> 01:30:08,730
Sorry.

828
01:30:12,490 --> 01:30:13,760
What are you doing?

829
01:31:23,670 --> 01:31:24,470
Let's go home.

830
01:31:25,850 --> 01:31:26,580
Let's go

831
01:31:28,500 --> 01:31:29,460
This way.

832
01:31:30,940 --> 01:31:31,660
Why?

833
01:31:32,450 --> 01:31:33,680
I'm not going home.

834
01:31:34,580 --> 01:31:35,870
Just a little more.

835
01:31:50,320 --> 01:31:51,260
Are you okay?

836
01:31:56,920 --> 01:31:58,390
Hey, get up. Let's go home.

837
01:32:08,160 --> 01:32:09,120
Hey, boss.

838
01:32:09,120 --> 01:32:09,710
Yes?

839
01:32:09,970 --> 01:32:10,970
You're the best.

840
01:32:13,020 --> 01:32:14,110
I love you.

841
01:34:20,700 --> 01:34:21,680
It's time.

842
01:34:37,070 --> 01:34:37,620
Bye.

843
01:35:36,240 --> 01:35:39,780
The doctor says Mom is in critical condition.

844
01:35:40,340 --> 01:35:43,410
and most likely permanently disabled.

845
01:35:44,840 --> 01:35:47,390
I don't know yet how long

846
01:35:48,110 --> 01:35:49,450
I have to stay here.

847
01:35:51,180 --> 01:35:53,750
The hospital smell is unbearable.

848
01:35:55,060 --> 01:35:57,180
I tried to remember the smells of

849
01:35:57,700 --> 01:35:59,680
places where us three would hang out.

850
01:36:00,840 --> 01:36:01,470
But

851
01:36:02,950 --> 01:36:05,400
I can't remember any of it at all.

852
01:36:31,550 --> 01:36:33,000
Let's get going.

853
01:36:39,790 --> 01:36:41,410
I got something to tell you.

854
01:36:50,950 --> 01:36:51,710
Okay.

855
01:37:03,260 --> 01:37:03,990
The thing is...

856
01:37:05,320 --> 01:37:08,080
I've decided to date Shizuo.

857
01:37:26,070 --> 01:37:27,240
I wanted to tell you properly.

858
01:37:30,490 --> 01:37:32,530
I could tell just by looking at you two.

859
01:37:43,450 --> 01:37:44,460
What's wrong?

860
01:37:46,210 --> 01:37:46,850
Nothing.

861
01:37:49,770 --> 01:37:51,260
I was just nervous.

862
01:37:55,620 --> 01:37:56,400
I see.

863
01:37:59,110 --> 01:38:00,010
You know.

864
01:38:06,370 --> 01:38:08,710
I was hoping you'd become a couple.

865
01:38:12,050 --> 01:38:14,700
Once Shizuo comes back from the hospital,

866
01:38:15,090 --> 01:38:17,760
perhaps I can feel a different side

867
01:38:18,160 --> 01:38:21,470
of Sachiko through Shizuo.

868
01:38:23,280 --> 01:38:29,360
I felt like I could be transparent, just like the air around them.

869
01:38:58,280 --> 01:38:59,070
Hey.

870
01:39:03,250 --> 01:39:05,540
I've been thinking a lot.

871
01:39:07,730 --> 01:39:09,510
I'm happy you met Shizuo.

872
01:39:24,690 --> 01:39:25,590
Take care.

873
01:39:29,640 --> 01:39:30,640
Ow! What?

874
01:39:31,960 --> 01:39:32,660
Goodbye.

875
01:40:02,930 --> 01:40:10,920
One, two, three, four, five,

876
01:40:12,470 --> 01:40:21,250
six, seven, eight, nine, ten,

877
01:40:22,650 --> 01:40:27,240
11, 12, 13...

878
01:40:35,030 --> 01:40:35,880
Sachiko!

879
01:40:40,830 --> 01:40:41,670
What?

880
01:40:44,910 --> 01:40:46,220
I just lied.

881
01:40:47,160 --> 01:40:48,080
About everything.

